U.S. Securities and Exchange
Commission Chairman Mary Jo White called on equity exchanges to
work together to identify concrete measures to address specific
areas where the resilience of market systems can be improved.  White made the remarks in a statement following a meeting
with the exchanges today in  Washington .  To contact the reporter on this story:
